    ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
    │                                                                     │
    │  Network Specialist,                                                │
    │                                                                     │
    │  Helios Station has suffered a cascade failure in our primary      │
    │  network infrastructure. Solar flare activity has corrupted our    │
    │  routing tables and disrupted communications between sectors.      │
    │                                                                     │
    │  As our only qualified network engineer currently on-station,      │
    │  you must diagnose and restore our network systems before the      │
    │  next resupply window closes in 72 hours.                          │
    │                                                                     │
    │  You have been granted access to our isolated training network -   │
    │  a containerized simulation of the station's infrastructure.       │
    │  Master these systems before attempting repairs on production.     │
    │                                                                     │
    │  NEXUS, our Network Expert System, will assist you. She has        │
    │  extensive knowledge of networking protocols and can provide       │
    │  hints if you get stuck.                                           │
    │                                                                     │
    │  The station is counting on you.                                   │
    │                                                                     │
    │  - Commander Chen                                                   │
    │                                                                     │
    └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘

