    │         infrastructure.                                             │
    │                                                                     │
    │         The training lab simulates our segmented architecture:     │
    │                                                                     │
    │         • FRONTEND ZONE (172.20.0.0/24)                            │
    │           Public-facing services, client access                    │
    │                                                                     │
    │         • BACKEND ZONE (172.21.0.0/24)                             │
    │           Internal services, database systems                       │
    │                                                                     │
    │         You will progress through four training modules:           │
    │                                                                     │
    │         [1] COMM-BAY     Network Fundamentals                      │
    │         [2] DIAGNOSTIC   Troubleshooting                           │
    │         [3] JUNCTION     Docker Networks                           │
    │         [4] SECURITY     Isolation & Protection                    │
    │                                                                     │
    │         Each module contains missions that build your skills.      │
    │         Complete all modules to certify for production repairs.    │
    │                                                                     │
    │         Type ./start.sh to initialize the training environment.    │
    │         Then: docker exec -it client bash                          │
    │                                                                     │
    │         Good luck, Specialist.                                     │
